ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a848dc4701d662f43ae74107aca7ee40885a138","tid":834422,"uid":26771,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"好多年前嘅事，<br />\n仲係皆大歡喜時期。<br />\n見到佢同趙學而同幾個人係一間野度食飯，<br />\n嗰時仲細，見到演員好興奮就拉住老母沖埋去話想影相，<br />\n之後阮兆祥就起身同我合照咗。<br />\n趙學而就全程冇理過我，<br />\n因為細過睇完皆大歡喜就覺得個個演員真人都好nice好搞笑，<br />\n所以趙學而咁冷淡令我弱小心靈做成咗打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個諗返係阮兆祥唔想我煩到其他人先同我影張相打發我走，<br />\n所以我覺得佢應該係好人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce0fc71bed5aaed68ec8f188e24175a09ca94af","tid":834422,"uid":18772,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"大撚鑊<br />\n打手黎吹奏即係好快又見到佢"},{"pid":"917cf62c1815c4bd89fdb1cc22d7617707d6e618","tid":834422,"uid":49359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:16:22.000Z","msg":"條仆街逆線行駛唔夠一排架車燒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d47f0cbe88a94bfeaaa32fdedbbe05fb2ba9bc6","tid":834422,"uid":68661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"馬路炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c014974874dfa3507815305d34136940f0e9d1fa","tid":834422,"uid":20430,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"6年左右有次行街路過見到拍戲，當時應該未開機<br />\n咁我地一班人，路途上要路過附近時見到佢，眼神有一下接觸後，個樣真係黑面到好似唔望得佢咁。<br />\n自始就對佢印象唔太喜歡"},{"pid":"1192fb0fb65199f48ac38bae0bc0fb0afe4a5289","tid":834422,"uid":211757,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:39:15.000Z","msg":"樓主gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f79e8411a4a7ef9a50ece2204dfa2f2fb8b6bb0","tid":834422,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:41:16.000Z